title: Candy Challenge v1.0 (Samsung Apps)
description:
Your Candy world is in danger. Evil vegetables have infiltrated your personal candy warehouse. 

It's time to take your guns and protect your candy world against the evil vegetables. Be careful and watch the friendly fire!

Features:

- Multiplayer with up to 4 Players 
- Play with your friends in coop or death-match mode
- 20 challenging arenas
- Choose between 4 characters
- Delicious levels mad by delicious candies!
- Easy play and fun!
